## Limitations

This report is limited by the availability of sources and the potential bias in the selected articles. The perspectives included are primarily from Western sources, which may not fully represent global viewpoints on the issue. Additionally, the rapidly evolving nature of this debate means that new developments may not be captured in this report. Further research could include more diverse perspectives and recent updates on the status of Confederate monuments.